  "title": "Business Support Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Jobscope:</strong></p><ul><li>Providing administrative support to director</li><li>Oversee the business support team across different entities/subsidiaries</li><li>Streamline the SOPs/processes for the different entities</li><li>Preparation of all management reports (Sales figures, Operations statistics etc)</li><li>Preparation of Delivery Schedule</li><li>Vetting through all official contracts</li><li>Support in HR Matters</li><li>Check and ensure the new items created are in order</li><li>And any other work as may be allocated at the discretion of the Management</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>· Min Degree/Diploma</p><p>· Min 5 years of relevant experience</p><p>· Willing to work under fast paced environment</p><p>· Must be meticulous with work</p><p>· Able to speak fluent English</p>",
